ote><br />\n唔用民族,用家黎講,你覺得個仔食到女威d定個女被仔食威d?</blockquote><br />\n唔係話食到鬼妹等於,而係食到外族,古代戰勝國都係會搶女人,有征服既意思,你有幾可聽過戰勝國既女人會揾番戰敗國既男人</blockquote><br />\n原來你係古代人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係外國人眼中係個鬼妹食你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34aa397fe8733a2feaf730146c167d30cd78e3f0","tid":380554,"uid":44267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"人地叫得你你唔係唔去啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個鬼妹都知咩事架喇，唔係你諗住佢想嫁比你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6755b330f52f8d3fa2d19597bfcd0c7ba6feca30","tid":380554,"uid":91014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"咪撚ff啦"},{"pid":"50cb380f5a0f4174e12b21d7cd119361ec0d3219","tid":380554,"uid":125218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"好愛你女朋友就唔會上黎開post 問<br />\n你個心根本已經動搖左 正仆街仔"},{"pid":"1338159ec7d6b4fc0a0614fdf9b66cfbdbe11cc6","tid":380554,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講低詳細經過 等我去啦<br />\n外國人睇我地 個個都差唔多樣 唔會認得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083daf29f223d5b7eeb55a9bc75619c22150e88b","tid":380554,"uid":42243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:22:40.000Z","msg":"人地想要你個腎咋懞佬"},{"pid":"c65ff51c3d3f1e9368790a22e430a026d3bfd018","tid":380554,"uid":15125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"問得出姐係你想去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a351fa9525b6570081f30955c27c5a3469098d","tid":380554,"uid":73722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"