.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你覺得屌人威d定比人屌威d呀on9</blockquote><br />\n大把人想屌鬼妹 <br />\n咁其實係咪鬼妹最威？<br />\n主導權係佢到喎 除非你強姦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔用民族,用家黎講,你覺得個仔食到女威d定個女被仔食威d?</blockquote><br />\n唔係話食到鬼妹等於,而係食到外族,古代戰勝國都係會搶女人,有征服既意思,你有幾可聽過戰勝國既女人會揾番戰敗國既男人</blockquote><br />\n原來你係古代人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係外國人眼中係個鬼妹食你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你up乜撚野呀,咪撚戇鳩啦,真係唔屌唔安樂,駁屌咪你呢種囉死戇鳩仔</blockquote><br />\n發爛渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc96c91d5290910831b09d5ec8a59f4e3a4c27d7","tid":380554,"uid":71726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:11:03.000Z","msg":"屌西屌到征服外族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb92156f3d5af91fd5e84730cc1116fa5b40c7a9","tid":380554,"uid":16516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"老閪都去"},{"pid":"5ee3fd3c70364d6590006980964ba533a934a875","tid":380554,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"飲下野姐 應酬下好正常"},{"pid":"5699d6ee6bd7b61b8d8ab54ad177921f494cd3d0","tid":380554,"uid":88888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男朋友一齊左3年<br />\n好穩定<br />\n但又毒又矮<br />\n不過勝在有錢，同錫我<br />\n<br />\n個鬼仔係旺角撞到<br />\n靚仔身材好<br />\n黎旅行<br />\n我幫佢帶路搵酒店<br />\n傾左一陣<br />\n佢後日走<br />\n問我聽日上唔上佢酒店到飲野<br />\n<br />\n如果係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負皮實多到仆街，所有留言都鬧臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/no